{"title":"麦收小记","authors":["李学鳌"],"dates":[{"year":1959,"month":6,"day":18}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"麦收小记"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李学鳌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喜讯"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听说帮农民麦收，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"顿时喜上心头。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来不及换掉工服，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞步向城外奔走。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"割麦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"麦穗沉甸甸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"镰刀亮闪闪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一手握麦一手镰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好一群“理发员”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只听喳喳响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"麦捆堆成山。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夸麦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金色麦穗黄又黄。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穗穗足有四寸长。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我同老农紧握手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一句话儿冲出腔："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把所有麦穗连成行，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也无法将咱们的友谊来衡量！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}